#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_fishing/init.lua:348
msgid "Fishing Rod"
msgstr "Arrantza-kanabera"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_fishing/init.lua:349
msgid "Catches fish in water"
msgstr "Harrapatu arrainak uretan"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_fishing/init.lua:350
msgid "Fishing rods can be used to catch fish."
msgstr "Kanaberak arrantzarako erabil daitezke."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_fishing/init.lua:351
msgid ""
"Rightclick to launch the bobber. When it sinks right-click again to reel in "
"an item. Who knows what you're going to catch?"
msgstr ""
"Egin eskuin-klik bobberra hasteko. Hondoratzen zarenean, egin eskuin-klik "
"berriro elementu bat biribilkatzeko. Nork daki zer harrapatuko duzun?"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_fishing/items.lua:4
msgid "Raw Fish"
msgstr "Bakailao gordina"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_fishing/items.lua:5
msgid ""
"Raw fish is obtained by fishing and is a food item which can be eaten "
"safely. Cooking it improves its nutritional value."
msgstr ""
"Bakailao gordina arrantzan lortzen da eta modu seguruan jan daitekeen "
"elikagaia da. Sukaldaritzak nutrizio-balioa hobetzen du."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_fishing/items.lua:13
msgid "Cooked Fish"
msgstr "Bakailao kozinatua"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_fishing/items.lua:14
msgid "Mmh, fish! This is a healthy food item."
msgstr "Mmh, arraina! Hau elikagai osasungarria da."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_fishing/items.lua:21
msgid "Raw Salmon"
msgstr "Izokin gordina"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_fishing/items.lua:22
msgid ""
"Raw salmon is obtained by fishing and is a food item which can be eaten "
"safely. Cooking it improves its nutritional value."
msgstr ""
"Izokin gordina arrantzan lortzen da, eta modu seguruan jan daitekeen "
"elikagaia da. Sukaldaritzak nutrizio-balioa hobetzen du."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_fishing/items.lua:30
msgid "Cooked Salmon"
msgstr "Prestatutako izokina"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_fishing/items.lua:31
msgid "This is a healthy food item which can be eaten."
msgstr "Jan daitekeen elikagai osasungarria da hau."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_fishing/items.lua:38
msgid "Clownfish"
msgstr "Pailazo arraina"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_fishing/items.lua:39
msgid ""
"Clownfish may be obtained by fishing (and luck) and is a food item which can "
"be eaten safely."
msgstr ""
"Arrain tropikala arrantzan lor daiteke (eta zorionez) eta modu seguruan jan "
"daitekeen elikagaia da."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_fishing/items.lua:46
msgid "Pufferfish"
msgstr "Globo-arraina"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_fishing/items.lua:47
msgid "Very poisonous"
msgstr "Oso pozoitsua"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_fishing/items.lua:48
msgid ""
"Pufferfish are a common species of fish and can be obtained by fishing. They "
"can technically be eaten, but they are very bad for humans. Eating a "
"pufferfish only restores 1 hunger point and will poison you very badly "
"(which drains your health non-fatally) and causes serious food poisoning "
"(which increases your hunger)."
msgstr ""
"Globo-arraina arrain-espezie arrunta da, eta arrantzaren bidez lor daiteke. "
"Teknikoki jan daitezke, baina gizakientzat oso txarrak dira. Puxika-arrain "
"bat jateak gose-puntu bat lehengoratzen du eta asko pozoitzen zaitu (zure "
"osasuna drainatzen du modu ez zorigaitzean) eta elikadura-intoxikazio larria "
"eragiten du (horrek gosea areagotzen dizu)."
